'''[[equivalence]] [[class]]''' (''plural'' '''equivalence classes''')

#{{settheory}} Any one of the [[subset]]s into which an [[equivalence relation]] [[partition]]s a [[set]], each of these subsets containing all the elements of the set that are equivalent under the equivalence relation.

